name: DynamO 1.7.3
body: This is a bugfix for the visualizer.

name: DynamO 1.7.2 release
body: This is just a maintenance release. There's some bug-fixes for visualisation, along with some small usability fixes in the code.

name: DynamO 1.7 release
body:
This release is the first where Windows and Mac OSX are supported. 

All of the builds used for testing on each platform are available below; however, OSX and Linux have highly variable libraries and you may have to compile yourself!

The zip and msi/deb packages all contain the same thing. Just use whichever package/install method is most convenient to you.

name: DynamO 1.5.0 Stable Release
body: The latest stable release of DynamO (December 2013).
